dct_title_s: Greenland--west coast, Sermersuut to Nunap Isua (Kap Farvel) (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From Danish charts to 1987."
